 uses a different currency for payments, you need to specify a conversion rate to convert the shipping cost returned by the shipping service into your store\'s currency. If the same currency is used, leave this set to 1.','en'),(312,287,'Domestic U.S.P.S.','','en'),(313,288,'Container','','en'),(314,289,'First-Class mail type','','en'),(315,290,'Pricing type to be used','','en'),(316,291,'Parcel type','','en'),(317,292,'Request rates for','','en'),(318,293,'International U.S.P.S.','','en'),(319,294,'Mail type','','en'),(320,295,'Get commercial base postage','','en'),(321,296,'Global Express Guarantee (GXG)','','en'),(322,297,'GXG destination is a post office box','','en'),(323,298,'GXG package contains a gift','','en'),(324,299,'Parcel type','','en'),(325,300,'Cash on delivery','','en'),(326,301,'Use a fixed amount Collect on Delivery fee','If you are planning to allow your customers to use the COD payment method for orders shipped with USPS shipping methods, you can make the calculation of shipping costs faster by setting a fixed extra fee for using the COD payment method.<br /><br />If a fixed amount COD fee is not set on the store\'s end, it will be calculated on the USPS end, and to get information about the COD fee amount the store will need to send several requests to the USPS API (one for each USPS service type), which may take up to 14 seconds. When using a fixed amount COD fee, the store will only send a single request to the USPS API, which will take under one second.<br /><br />Using a <b>fixed amount COD fee</b> allows the store to calculate the shipping cost much faster and is the <b>recommended option</b>.','en'),(327,302,'Fixed COD price','If you have selected to use a fixed COD fee, specify the fee amount here. The COD fee will be used for all shipping methods returned by the USPS server.<br /><br />You can find the current price for the USPS Collect on Delivery (COD) extra service on this page: <a href=\"https://www.usps.com/business/add-extra-services.htm\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.usps.com/business/add-extra-services.htm</a>','en'),(328,303,'Additional options','','en'),(329,304,'Log all communication between shopping cart and USPS server','','en'),(330,305,'Sandbox mode','','en'),(331,306,'Auto enable new USPS shipping methods','','en'),(332,275,'Data provider','','ru'),(333,276,'PitneyBowes merchant emailId','','ru'),(334,277,'PitneyBowes merchant shipperId','','ru'),(335,278,'Идентификатор пользователя','','ru'),(336,279,'Веб-адрес API сервера U.S.P.S.','Введите веб-адрес, указанный в уведомлении от U.S.P.S. об успешной регистрации в U. S. Postal Service Web Tools Application Program Interfaces. Например: <ul><li>http://testing.shippingapis.com/ShippingAPITest.dll</li><li>http://production.shippingapis.com/ShippingAPI.dll</li></ul>','ru'),(337,280,'Дополнительные настройки','','ru'),(338,281,'Общие настройки','','ru'),(339,282,'Размеры упаковки (в дюймах)','If dimensions are not provided, Web Tools will assume package is regular in size and all dimensions are less than or equal to 12 inches.','ru'),(340,283,'Периметр (дюймы)','Для больших размеров и непрямоугольного и неизменяемого контейнера.','ru'),(341,284,'Максимальный вес упаковки','','ru'),(342,286,'Коэффициент пересчета валюты','Укажите ставку X, где 1 USD = X в валюте магазина.<br/>Стоимость доставки всегда определяется в американских доллрах. Если в магазине используется другая валюта, необходимо указать коэффициент пересчёта стоимости доставки, полученной от службы доставки, в валюту магазина. Если валюта совпадает, оставить коэффициент равным 1.','ru'),(343,287,'Локальный U.S.P.S.','','ru'),(344,288,'Тара','','ru'),(345,289,'Тип почтового отправления для сервиса First-Class','','ru'),(346,285,'Машинная обработка','','ru'),(347,290,'Используемый тип цены (розничная, коммерческая и т.п.)','','ru'),(348,291,'Тип почтового отправления','','ru'),(349,293,'Международная служба U.S.P.S.','','ru'),(350,294,'Тип почтового отправления','','ru'),(351